<br>
I have been threatened by people to train me and my guild (after I let them past to kill one named mob as they said and then they decided to take the camp we were sitting outside of) from now and into the future, just because they were so greedy and couldn't learn the word &quot;share&quot; or &quot;maturity.&quot;  This person swore at me and &quot;personally&quot; threatened me in tells (reported) and remained clearing the area that we were about to camp before we kindly as a guild stepped aside to let them kill the named mob.  When I tried to resolve the issue privately in tells and was ignored, I asked the same question in /ooc &quot;Since you are done killing Vindi, will you be leaving the Arena now?.&quot;  This is what brought the threats to my guild, and me personally (although I don't know how someone can personally threaten someone 5K miles away).<br>
<br>
Neither of these issues were ever resolved and I see these people playing every day, upsetting more people and getting their slaps on the wrist.<br>
